&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/9326271635197046152.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-182342/images/9326271635197046152.jpg" src="projects/project-182342/images/9326271635197046152.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
